        </param>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="classmrmeshpy_1_1EdgeId" kindref="compound">EdgeId</ref></type>
          <declname>e</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>given the edge with left and right triangular faces, which form together a quadrangle,
rotates the edge counter-clockwise inside the quadrangle;
the length of e becomes equal to the length of geodesic line between its new ends on original mesh;
does not flip and returns false if the geodesic line does not go fully inside the quadrangle
</verbatim> </para>
